    "long_instructions": "## Marketing Research Chat\r\n\r\nHave one person in your group make a copy of the **[template](https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1oKz0lKygs6NsKqrO1HSiH2JRAWXtLT4uQEw8F18mwY0/template/preview).**  \r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to do some market research for your product or app. \r\n\r\nFocus on ideas that connect to your assigned role (e.g., name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to do some market research for your product or app.\r\n    - What do people in your target audience want or need in a product like this?\r\n    - What everyday challenges or frustrations could this product solve?\r\n    - What existing solutions already try to meet these needs? How does yours stand out?\r\n    - Are there images, examples, or documents you can share with AI to spark better ideas?\r\n2. Want better results? Try asking AI about a specific audience—for example:\r\n   - busy professionals working from home\r\n   - parents balancing work and family life\r\n   - adults trying to simplify their daily routines",
